Title : Bartolomeu Constantin Săvoiu
Text : {{Underlinked|date=May 2014}}
[[File:Bartolomeu Constantin Săvoiu.jpg|thumb|Bartolomeu Constantin Săvoiu]]

'''Bartolomeu Constantin Săvoiu''' (born 18 February 1945 in Bucharest) is a general in the reserves of the [[Romanian Land Forces]], as well as, within the [[Freemasonry in Romania|Romanian freemasonry]], head of the ''Romanian National Grand Lodge - 1880''. He is also a [[France|French]] citizen.<ref>{{ro icon}} Ondine Gherguț, [http://www.romanialibera.ro/politica/institutii/venerabilul-mason--generalul-savoiu-din-partidul-rezervistilor-serviciilor-secrete---voiculescu--becali--psd--pnl-sunt-praduitori---vezi-despre-cine-a-spus-ca-e-cinstit-295488 "Venerabilul mason, generalul Săvoiu din partidul rezerviştilor serviciilor secrete: 'Voiculescu, Becali, PSD, PNL sunt prăduitori'. Vezi despre cine a spus că e cinstit"], ''România Liberă'', March 7, 2013; accessed June 26, 2014</ref> In 2017, he became president of a new political party, the Alliance Law and Order. A center-right party, its stated goal is the defence of the national identity of Romania, of the Judeo-Christian common religious roots and heritage, of Western society and of Judeo-Christian Europe.

